        "username": "bougetq"
      },
      "date": "2018-05-09 14:36:24.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n\nThis is basically the same patch as the one Sebastien submitted (https://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/30943) except it is rebased on top of https://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/31613/ which provides some utility functions to parse and look for changelog records.\n\nI only changed what was needed to get rid of \"changelog_setup\" / \"changelog_cleanup\" / \"changelog_get_flags\".\n\nThis also means that tests 600, 604 and 606 fail in the same way: \"nid '0@lo' does not match any client NID: 10.200.0.1@tcp\"",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
